name: "Little People" 12" clock Navy or Red
description:
This beautiful fabric wall clock in a 12 inch wooden frame was handmade in Victoria. The playful clock design will both brighten and complement your child’s bedroom, nursery, playroom, or even the kitchen! The clock is both stylish and functional; the fabrics are hand-picked, and every clock is hand-made.  As such there are slight variations to each clock making them all the more special and unique. This gorgeous Roslyn Road clock would make an ideal gift for a newborn, birthday, Christening or Christmas.

Roslyn Road clock mechanisms are covered by a 10 year manufacturer's warranty with your proof of purchase.

Colours avaliable Navy, Red, Blue, Pink & Beige
